      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "TOUSLED CROWN (1) comes back in trip today off a short freshen, beaten 2.6L after sitting up on the speed in a stronger race at Pinjarra last time out. Li's 4kg claim comes in handy and she is a winner over this trip previously. Can be prominent in the run and take beating. MISSILE GIRL (3) disappointed last start but was better two runs back at York when winning a BM44+. The inside draw is a big tick today and should see her sit much closer than we saw last time out. Better suited here and can bounce back to winning ways. OSCAR WINNER (5) was returning from a break last time out and proved too classy, scoring by 2 lengths over 1200m at Rockingham. Open to plenty of improvement and this looks well within his grasp. TORQUED UP (7) was last at the races when he finished eighth over 1200m at Broome on August 16. Sure to make his presence felt. IMPERIALIZE (4) won't be far away if he can run up to his recent form.",
